Surf_helium

Its finally done!

A 6 stage skill map based off the hit map surf_hydrogen.

The map is on a 5 minute timer, and when it expires (if noone beats the map) people will be teleported to jail and receive the following weapons (different for t and ct)

lv1- knife
lv2- pistol
lv3- tmp/mac10
lv4- galil/famas
lv5- ak/m4
lv6- awp

if beaten, the winner will be taken to an area and have a choice of para, or blades.

max. 36 players

SPECIAL THANKS TO KNIFE FOR THE JAIL AND HELP ALONG THE WAY <33

thanks to intox. clan

thanks to zalos for nofalldmg fixing

have fun playing!
